R --> UC2
R --> UC3
R --> UC4
R --> UC7
R --> UC10
R --> UC11
R --> UC15
R --> UC16
R --> UC17
R --> UC18

' Game System associations for background auto-executed use cases
GS --> UC4
GS --> UC5
GS --> UC6
GS --> UC8
GS --> UC9
GS --> UC12
GS --> UC13
GS --> UC14
GS --> UC27
GS --> UC28

